You are on the 1st tier of Imperial Reconquest, which grants CB on the core Byzantine lands.
column6: Estás en el 1er nivel de Reconquista Imperial, lo que otorga CBs en las principales tierras bizantinas.

column2: You are on the 2nd tier of Imperial Reconquest, which grants CB against the Balkans and Sicily.
column6: Estás en el 2do nivel de Reconquista Imperial, lo que otorga CBs contra los Balcanes y Sicilia.

column2: You are on the 3rd tier of Imperial Reconquest, which grants CB against the Levant, most of Italy (though not Lombardia), and Africa (but not Western or sub-saharan Africa).
column6: Estás en el 3er nivel de Reconquista Imperial, lo que otorga CBs contra el Levante, la mayor parte de Italia (sin Lombardía), y África (pero no el África occidental ni subsahariana).

column2: You are on the 4th tier of Imperial Reconquest, which grants CB against the rest of Italy (Lombardia), Northwest Africa, and Iberia.
column6: Estás en el 4to nivel de Reconquista Imperial, lo que otorga CBs contra el resto de Italia (Lombardía), el Noroeste de África e Iberia.

column2: You are on the 5th tier of Imperial Reconquest, which grants CB against Gallia / France.
column6: Estás en el 5to nivel de Reconquista Imperial, lo que otorga CBs contra las Galias / Francia.

column2: You are on the 6th tier of Imperial Reconquest-- the final Roman frontier, which grants CB against England, Wales, parts of Germania, and parts of Pannonia.
column6: Estás en el 6to nivel de Reconquista Imperial-- el final de la frontera romana, lo que otorga CBs contra Inglaterra, Gales, partes de Germania y partes de Panonia.
